                        <interp inst="t18350511-name-802" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE HART</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable G</hi> 116.) I was sent for, and found these three parcels of tea on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(The prisoner put in a written defence, stating that he had weighed the tea and sugar for his own use, and had put the amount it came to, into the till.)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18350511-name-803" type="witnessName">
